snippet.title: U-LifyTV
snippet.description:
U-lIFYTV Channel/Account is a MULTI-PURPOSE Online-Tv that mostly draws is attention on the challenges and limitations of the Youth in Nigeria. ulify tv is set to create solutions to the problems surrounding the youth through information, seminar or talk show, build a platform where the youth can develop there career, also we encourage the youth through several motivational programme we organised around Dreams are dying and young Nigerians are among frustrated groups on earth. Most of these young Nigerians, save those from rich homes, cannot acquire quality tertiary education as Nigerian universities are suffering from a reversal of fortunes. 
Across the world, youth have all the power to bring change in the whole world with the right life skills, vision & sense of assessment. The youth only want a proper guidance to sustain proactive solutions. So many youth out there whom may have possess some skill, talent, ideas
